QuestData.Title: Return to Oribos
QuestData.Description:
You have proven yourself a worthy ally of Bastion in your time here, $n. Though I wish you could remain here, there are other realms in the Shadowlands that require aid more.
Return to Oribos when you are able and seek out Tal-Inara. She will help you decide where to best next focus your efforts.
Archon watch over you.
QuestData.RewardText: You have fulfilled your purpose. Well done.
